  -gnome-bluetooth-0.12.0.ebuild:
  Removal of deprecated slot 0.

  22 Oct 2010; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  gnome-bluetooth-2.32.0.ebuild:
  Move nautilus-sendto la file removal behind nautilus USE flag.

